longBusinessSummary: iShares Trust - iShares Global Healthcare ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by BlackRock, Inc. It is managed by BlackRock Fund Advisors. It invests in public equity markets of global region. It invests in stocks of companies operating across health care sectors. The fund invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. It seeks to track the performance of the S&P Global 1200 Health Care Index, by using representative sampling technique. iShares Trust - iShares Global Healthcare ETF was formed on November 13, 2001 and is domiciled in the United States.
